rComments: Professor Craft is a fine lecturer, and he evidently knows a lot about the subject matter, but his classes can often hew too closely to the textbook, and as a result, aren't nearly as engaging or interesting as they could be. Still, a nice guy who knows a lot about Canadian politics.
The prof is trying his best. However, as a lecturer he is lackluster and cannot hold the attention of his student. Please start taking a break at the halfway point of a 2 hour lecture.
